MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a fault with the power in the G66 postcode area of Kirkintilloch. This is causing reduced power to a number of properties. We had no advance warning of this and only became aware of it at 6:39pm. Our engineers are on their way the local substation to investigate and our team will work to get your power back to normal as quickly and as safely as possible by 9:45pm. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 7:17pm on Tuesday, 27 October 2020
